text: Avdotyino () is a rural locality (a village) in Domodedovo District of Domodedovsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 152 as of 2010. There are 15 streets.Карта деревни Авдотьино в Московской области == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdotyino, Domodedovo, Moscow Oblast
